# ripgrep-specific ignore (gitignore syntax). ripgrep already skips paths in
# .gitignore and .git/; this file removes *content* noise from `rg` searches so
# a query for a shell pattern isn't drowned in legal or lockfile boilerplate.
#
# Precedence: .rgignore and .ignore override .gitignore for ripgrep. Nothing
# here is git-ignored — these files ARE tracked; they are only hidden from `rg`.
LICENSE
CHANGELOG.md

# Codex repo-scope skills are symlinks to skills/*; hide duplicate search hits.
.agents/skills/**

# Keep broad `rg` sweeps bounded (repo convention: never traverse VCS/data dirs).
.git/
